headline: Anthony Terrick Named Senior Director of Business Development at Global Risk Consultants
summary: WOODBRIDGE, N.J., October 15, 2025--Global Risk Consultants (GRC), the worldwide leader in independent property risk engineering, today announced that Anthony Terrick has been named Senior Director of Business Development at Global Risk Consultants.
